* Burn in the Spotlight Tour (2001–2002)
* Come as You Are Tour (2004)
* Get Loose Tour (2007–2008)
* Mi Plan Tour (2010)
* The Spirit Indestructible Tour (2013)
* Summer Tour (2017)

Co-headlining
* Area Festival (2001) 
* Art on Ice (2015)

Opening act
* Elevation Tour (2001)
* Musicology Live 2004ever (2004)

